WEBVTT

00:05.999 --> 00:07.730
Previously on Genius...

00:07.731 --> 00:11.147
I am Max Jacob.
Most days, I am a poet.

00:11.148 --> 00:13.526
That's even worse
than being a painter.

00:13.550 --> 00:16.869
I cannot bear the thought of
living in this world without you.

00:17.220 --> 00:18.931
Max, I love you.

00:18.955 --> 00:21.707
But not the way you want me to.

00:21.958 --> 00:24.003
They have sent the rest
of his family to the camps.

00:24.027 --> 00:27.446
You are the only one who
can persuade him to get out.

00:27.497 --> 00:29.709
We could take away
everything, and everyone.

00:29.733 --> 00:32.918
I am not a Jew anymore.
So, I am not leaving.

00:33.036 --> 00:35.621
This is my home. Here with God.

00:35.672 --> 00:38.251
You're a brilliant
photographer, Dora.

00:38.275 --> 00:41.320
There is a painter
trapped inside of you.

00:41.344 --> 00:43.356
Are you going to tell me
what you thought of my paintings?

00:43.380 --> 00:45.425
You have talent.

00:45.449 --> 00:47.047
You want to paint
something new and

00:47.071 --> 00:48.528
you think getting
this young girl into

00:48.552 --> 00:50.196
bed will help you do that.

00:50.220 --> 00:52.838
You're just jealous.

00:52.956 --> 00:54.634
Are you sure you are ready?

00:54.658 --> 00:56.536
Yes.

00:56.560 --> 00:59.605
I could
offer you work. As a model.

00:59.629 --> 01:01.374
That wasn't our agreement.

01:01.398 --> 01:03.983
If you don't like it, leave.

01:05.435 --> 01:07.847
Love can be dangerous.

01:07.871 --> 01:09.989
Fernande.

01:10.140 --> 01:12.658
If you ask me,
this will not end well.

